abt/\r\n3. Spoken Tutorial: Created Spoken tutorials on Aakash Business Tool(ABT) http://www.spoken-tutorial.org/. \r\nCurrently doing research and creating tutorials on BioPython.\r\n\r\nMy Interests : \r\n- Rubiks Cube\r\n- Blogging\r\n- Trekking\r\n- Chess\r\n- Teaching\r\n- Skating\r\n\r\nThis website will tell you everything about me - Personal, Projects, Start-Ups and Inspirations .Feel free to write to me through the contact me form on this website.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:1377:\"<p>Heya,<br />\nI am Trupti Kini, a Junior Programmer @ Indian Institute of Technology, Bombay with experiences in Python, Android, BioPython.<br />\nThanks for taking the time to visit my website!</p>\n<p>I\'m an Open Source Software Developer from Mumbai, India. I build, modify and hack technology to make it suitable for solving real world problems.<br />\nI am a hungry kid.....hunger to learn 24/7. Some of my work is inspired by those on the internet and the rest has been developed by me working in a team or alone. </p>\n<p>I\'m currently pursuing the Masters in FOSS @ Anna University in Chennai. </p>\n<p>The Projects I worked in :<br />\n1. GNUKhata: A FOSS Accounting Web Application in Python.<br />\n2. Aakash Tablet: Accounting Android Application named Aakash Business Tool <a href=\"http://aakashlabs.org/abt/\">http://aakashlabs.org/abt/</a><br />\n3. Spoken Tutorial: Created Spoken tutorials on Aakash Business Tool(ABT) <a href=\"http://www.spoken-tutorial.org/\">http://www.spoken-tutorial.org/</a>.<br />\nCurrently doing research and creating tutorials on BioPython.</p>\n<p>My Interests :<br />\n- Rubiks Cube<br />\n- Blogging<br />\n- Trekking<br />\n- Chess<br />\n- Teaching<br />\n- Skating</p>\n<p>This website will tell you everything about me - Personal, Projects, Start-Ups and Inspirations .Feel free to write to me through the contact me form on this website.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s: